{"id": 231972898, "title": "Local creatives celebrated, honoured at annual Windsor Mayor's Arts Awards", "text": "The event also included a special memoriam presentation honouring members of the arts community who passed away over the last two years. This year\u2019s categories and winners are: 2024 Windsor Mayor\u2019s Arts Awards Individual Artist \u2013 Marty Gervais. Arts Organization \u2013 Windsor Light Music Theatre. Arts Volunteer \u2013 Capitol Theatre Volunteer Group. 2024 WEA Arts Leadership Awards (Awards of Merit) Community Arts Leadership Award (Individual) \u2013 Bernadette Berthelotte. Community Arts Leadership Award (Organization) \u2013 Sh\u014d Studios. Literary Arts Leadership Award \u2013 Christopher Lawrence Menard. Performing Arts Music Leadership Award \u2013 Hugh and Kathy Leal. Performing Arts Theatre Leadership Award \u2013 Arts Collective Theatre (ACT). Visual Arts Leadership Award \u2013 Arts Council Windsor & Region (ACWR). 2024 WEA Emerging Artist Grant \u2013 ($3,000) Artist in Film Arts \u2013 Elissa Weir. Emerging Artist in Literary Arts \u2013 Erik Johnson. Emerging Artist in Performing Arts \u2013 Alysia Therrien. Lois Smedick Emerging Artist in Visual Arts \u2013 Tristan Olivier Balmokune. 2024 WEA Arts Infrastructure Grant \u2013 ($3,000)", "summary": "The spotlight shone on Windsor&#8217;s arts and culture sector last week, with over 20 artists, art organizations, and supporters being honoured at the Windsor Mayor&#8217;s Arts Awards. Mayor Drew Dilkens and Windsor Endowment for the Arts (WEA) president Stephanie Barnhard co-hosted the event held last Friday at Mackenzie Hall in Sandwich Towne.\u00a0 Each award recipient [&#8230;]", "url": "https://windsorstar.com/news/local-news/local-creatives-celebrated-honoured-at-annual-windsor-mayors-arts-awards", "image": "https://smartcdn.gprod.postmedia.digital/windsorstar/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/sho-studios-1.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 13:19:34", "author": "Millar Holmes-Hill", "authors": ["Millar Holmes-Hill"], "language": "en", "source_country": "ca", "sentiment": 0.867}